# ─── Runtime state (never commit) ─────────────────────────────────────────────
.sessions/

# ─── Machine-specific platform config ─────────────────────────────────────────
# detected.md is auto-generated at boot (B4) — template must stay platform: unknown
# Gitignore the file only if you want B4 to always re-detect on clone
# Current choice: commit as platform: unknown template
# .agents/platform/detected.md

# ─── Project-specific indexes (regenerated per project) ────────────────────────
knowledge/index_files.json
knowledge/index_variables.json
knowledge/error_index.md
knowledge/index_sessions.json

# ─── Session history / runtime logs ────────────────────────────────────────────
knowledge/harness_flow_*.md
knowledge/cfp_archive.md

# ─── macOS resource forks ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
._*
.DS_Store

# ─── Python ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
